
# Tic-Tac-Toe

Tic Tac Toe is a two-player game in which the objective is to take turns and mark the correct spaces in a 3x3 (or larger) grid.

## Run Locally

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/krunalbhandekar/Tic-Tac-Toe
```
Install

```bash
 npm install or npm i
```

Run

```bash
 npm start
```
